OL,4,CCovid: UK's furlough scheme starts to
OL,5,Cwind down
OL,6, More than a million workers came off
OL,7, furlough in May as the economy
OL,8, reopened, leaving the scheme supporting
OL,9, the fewest people since the start of
OL,10, the pandemic.
OL,12,FAt the end of May, 2.4 million people
OL,13,Fstill relied on the scheme for their
OL,14,Fincome, the latest HMRC figures show.
OL,16,FThe furlough measures are being phased
OL,17,Fout by the end of September.
OL,19,FBut with parts of the economy still
OL,20,Flimited by the virus, some firms are
OL,21,Fcalling for an extension to the scheme.
